OL,9,GScience Week, where science,           
OL,10,Gengineering and technology will be     
OL,11,Gcelebrated nationwide. For details of  
OL,12,Gevents in your area, and all over the  
OL,13,Gcountry, call the British Association  
OL,14,Gof the Advancement of Science on       
OL,15,G0171 973 3076.                         
